    A message containing arbitrary data to be used by the KeybasedRouting.sendMessage method
    ContentRequest
    A message containing arbitrary data to be used by the KeybasedRouting.sendRequest methods

    A message containing arbitrary data to be used by the KeybasedRouting.sendRequest methods
    FindNodeRequest
    A findNode request as defined in the kademlia protocol
    FindNodeResponse
    A findNode response as defined in the kademlia protocol

    PingResponse
    A ping response as defined in the kademlia protocol
    ShadesFindNodeRequest
    A findNode request as defined in the kademlia protocol
    ShadesFindNodeResponse
    A findNode response as defined in the kademlia protocol in shades, our response should contain a list of correctly shaded nodes.
    StoreMessage
    A store results message to be inserted to the destination node's cache
